# Trivy ignore file for reducing false positives

# Development and test files
**/*test*
**/*spec*
**/*mock*
**/node_modules/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**.md

# Generated files
**/coverage/**
**/.turbo/**
**/.next/**

# Config files that may contain example secrets
**/wrangler.jsonc
**/package.json
**/tsconfig.json

# Ignore example/placeholder values
# Example: ignore this specific test secret
# secret-id-here

